wiki.summary: "Stuck with U" is a song by American singer Ariana Grande and Canadian singer Justin Bieber. It was released as a charity single on May 8, 2020.[1] The song marks the second time both artists collaborated following a remix of Bieber's 2015 single "What Do You Mean?". According to their manager Scooter Braun who also co-wrote the track, the song is the first of more charity singles to be released throughout 2020. Read more on Last.fm.
